UNITED STATES; UNITED STATES -- POLITICS; BUSH, GEORGE; UNITED STATES -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; INTEREST RATES; PUBLIC OPINION; UNITED STATES -- ECONOMY; 
GOVERNMENT SPENDING 
</P>
