This diner/drugstore in the heart of Old Towne Orange is a real throwback. 
True, the bobby-soxers are gone and the drugstore no longer fills prescriptions 
for whiskey, but the malts still come thick, rich and big enough to share, and 
meals are the kind Mom might've made. MARY HELEN BERG 
