<P>
COLLEGE NEWS: PCC TO SPONSOR INFORMATION NIGHT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Pasadena City College will sponsor college information night in Room 200, 
Building D on the campus, 1570 E. Colorado Blvd., from 5 to 7 p.m. Tuesday, 
Oct. 30. 
</P>
<P>
The program gives those who want to earn a bachelor's degree an opportunity to 
meet with university representatives and receive information on admissions, 
program requirements, tuition and financial aid. 
